'''達爾文樹皮蛛'''（{{lang-en|'''Darwin's bark spider'''}}；學名：{{lang|la|'''''Caerostris darwini'''''}}；有些華文媒體譯作「達爾文吠蛛」但應為誤譯）是目前已知可建構最大[[圓網蜘蛛#圓網|圓網（orb web）]]的[[圓網蜘蛛|圓網蜘蛛（orb-weaving spider）]]，其網結構的總橫幅可達25公尺。該物種被發現於[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]的[[Andasibe-Mantadia國家公園|Andasibe-Mantadia國家公園]]<ref name="BBC">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/earth/hi/earth_news/newsid_9001000/9001866.stm |title=Gigantic spider's web discovered in Madagascar |author=Matt Walker |date=16 September 2010 |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |accessdate=17 September 2010 |archive-date=2019-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190131093253/http://news.bbc.co.uk/earth/hi/earth_news/newsid_9001000/9001866.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2009年被命名為自然學者[[達爾文|達爾文]]的姓名以紀念其著作《[[物種原始|物種原始]]》出版150週年<ref name="Arachnology">{{cite journal |author=Matjaž Kuntner & Ingi Agnarsson |year=2010 |title=Web gigantism in Darwin's bark spider, a new species from Madagascar (Araneidae: ''Caerostris'') |journal=[[The_Journal_of_Arachnology|The Journal of Arachnology]] |publisher=American Arachnological Society |volume=38 |pages=346–356 |url=http://www.nephilidae.com/mk/articles/Kuntner&Agnarsson2010.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |access-date=2022-02-11 |archive-date=2011-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714164015/http://www.nephilidae.com/mk/articles/Kuntner%26Agnarsson2010.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

